The 700 runs a little tight the 9 1/2 was too loose for me but the 9 fit little tight but I've been using it and tru is yeezys are comfortable i wish kanye would consider making all yeezys as comfortable as the 350 because I feel the 360 put the yeezys where they are and in my case I would pay for comfort and quality any time I love the design on my yeezys 700 the colors the soles should have been as comfortable as the 350 and the fit I would have given it a 5 start rattling.I haven't liked any of the yeezys 350 v2 I don't know maybe I will try the new ones... but I like the original version best...maybe kanye will come back with all the colors options this time that will be awesome.
